 attacks carefully. I think this would be difficult to teach the player. I would test it on other players who haven's seen the video and see if they can manage.</div><br /><br />As I said before looking to get out a bit of the norm, some enemies require some strategy, others are more simple, just hopefully not be too difficult.<br /><br />I think if you could do for NES, it would have to do without some effects like sun and others but I think it could look good.<br /><br />Pardon my English and thanks for convey their impressions, I have in mind!.<br /><br />Como dije antes buscaba salirme un poco de la norma habitual, algunos enemigos requieren cierta estrategia, otros son mas sencillos, solo espero que no resulten demasiado dificiles.<br /><br />Perdonen mi ingles y gracias por transmitirme sus impresiones, las tengo en cuenta!.

		

